Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:55.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Guess I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:36.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy that farce?\NPretending to be the evil Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:40.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:47.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to be the villain.\NI'm glad I got to do it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You went easy on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:51.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did I, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:54.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb! You let my spell hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:59.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Should I have dodged it?\NYou guys were losing pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You wanted to lose, from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You came here hoping we would defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:16.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can't say it all went according to plan,\Nbut you did disable me before I killed everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:21.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your little game nearly took the lives\Nof all five of us, you bloody fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:28.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,From the start? When would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How far back does that go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I asked you before why you joined us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:37.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If humanity had betrayed you,\Nor you wanted to put an end to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:42.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,or if you'd come seeking a place to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a foolish answer this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:50.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now, this belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:57.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I used an emergency override\Nto cut me off from the Stone's energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:01.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've only got 300 seconds, so don't dilly-dally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can only do this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:07.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So we just pull it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:12.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yep. It's in pretty tight,\Nbut it's just like popping a cap off a bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:20.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No! Don't! Please don't kill Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:25.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Echidna! Don't kill him, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:29.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come, Lily, don't make a fuss. Queen Echidna is unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No! Leo, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look at that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:48.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Till the very end, he's protecting humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:55.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He was never going to kill anyone or destroy our worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:05:01.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He knew he could sacrifice his life to bring\Npeace to both and willingly made that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:08.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It pains me to admit it, but he truly is a hero,\Nthrough and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,270 seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you have any regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:22.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Someone's picking up my work,\Nand the Demon Army's running more efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:27.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everything's good. I've got no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:30.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:34.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop this tantrum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:50.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Demon World needs the Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's one last thing I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,240 seconds, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:32.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Great Generals. Goodbye, Echidna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:37.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I got to know you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:44.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:47.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind. It's too much effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:48.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:52.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You want me to make peace with the human world?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:58.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You fool! Have you forgotten who I am?\NI am the Demon Queen, the great Echidna!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:01.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am the ruler of the Demon World, its queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:06.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you know how busy I am?\NI've no time for this errand of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:08.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:13.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now listen, hero... No, now you're merely Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Listen, Leo, and rejoice, for I have decided\Nto officially employ you in my ranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:24.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Seeing as you possess the Stone and\Nare the only being to have lived 3000 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:27.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I appoint you as ambassador between\Nthe Demon and Human worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?! You're running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:30.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd expect nothing less of you, My Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:38.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,H-hey, Edvard! Talk some sense into her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:40.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, screw that, tear the Stone out of me, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Leo, surely you jest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:49.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I agree with Queen Echidna.\NYou'd best give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You only have 200 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:55.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are still so many things I'd like to learn from\Nyou, Lord Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:59.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your death would be a great disservice! To me, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How is he this stupid?! It makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:11.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can you think of any other better to unite\Nour worlds than a man who's lived 3000 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:12.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:21.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And my darling Julietta has taken quite a liking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:24.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What father would I be if I made her cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:28.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I beseech you, reconsider your decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:30.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you not have a brain inside that thick skull of yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're the one without a brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:36.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why did you think of this by yourself\Nso you can end it by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:39.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ask your friends for help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You didn't ask me for help at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why? Who could I have--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:54.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You taught me that when you're in trouble,\Nyou should ask your friends for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You taught me that when\Nyou can't do it by yourself to find, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:01.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I get it, Lily! One of my shortcomings\Nis my inability to trust people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.21,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Find the right person for the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:05.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But this isn't the time for this! You have 160 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.00,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,So why are you doing this?! Look at me and tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:16.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid, so I don't know why you want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:22.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I'll always hear you out,\Nso please don't die on me, you big dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:30.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernes! He'll be able to calmly analyze the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:35.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've only got 140 seconds left. I trust you, Mernes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You won't let your emotions get the better of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:38.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,OW!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:41.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:40.96,Subtitle-4,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That hurts! Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:48.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I didn't need to be a good listener.\NI just needed to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:55.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your words, your attitude, your eyes,\Neverything is screaming that you want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This whole time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then live, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you want to live, then live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:09.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You told me to make choices you won't regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:14.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But here you are, dying full of regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You only have 110 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:18.29,Subtitle-4,,0,0,0,,Moron! Idiot! Imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:19.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shutina! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Help with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:30.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, have you caught on to\Nthe contradiction in your words?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:31.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-what contradiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:35.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tell me, for what reason are you dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What? I don't have time to--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:43.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To protect humanity. That's the order they built into us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:46.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And none of the Demonhart Series can disobey it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:50.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Another order, Thought Masking, erases\Nany rebellious thoughts before they develop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You only have 95 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But in your case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes! I developed, I grew a strong ego, a self!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That self turned off my Thought Masking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I can't keep my identity if I don't protect humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:07.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If something doesn't change, I'm going to\Nput humanity in danger just so I can save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:11.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's just how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:16.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No matter how strong my ego or sense of free will,\Nthey're not strong enough to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:25.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,By that logic, your strong ego should allow you\Nto disable your order to protect, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What? No, it couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:28.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Try it, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:42.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Disable the order?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:55.96,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil. Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Disable THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:58.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is she stupid?! I've been following this order\Nfor 3000 years! I can't just turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.71,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil. Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:04.42,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil. Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:05.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How am I even supposed to do that?\NJust "try it"? Help me out, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:10.50,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil. Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:07.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It can't be done! I don't know how!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:16.25,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil. Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I get it, but could you shut up for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:22.08,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil. Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just stop, please stop, just STOP.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.13,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,Protect hum-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:26.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:38.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I disabled it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:44.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I HAVE TO protect the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I HAVE TO be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:52.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There was no way to escape those compulsions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:57.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did I just CONVINCE myself that I HAD to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, there are 30 seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you truly want to die, then I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:08.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's your life. Use it as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:14.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know shit about bioweapons,\Nbut you should live your life the way you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:19.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But if you want to live, then do not waste\Nyour life trapped by someone else's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:25.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't get too caught up in\Nthis 'born to protect humanity' shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:29.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Humanity has exiled you.\NIs this not the perfect opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:35.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Work under me, and leave 'heroing'\Nbehind for a new way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:40.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If humanity stops needing you, that's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:44.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Find something else to live for, and enjoy your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:56.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Quit heroing and join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your three thousand years of endless solitude end now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:57.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Boy, you guys really let your guards down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:59.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Foolish indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sharing wine with the Hero Leo,\Nthen falling asleep in his presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Had you told me of this before, I would have laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:11.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't see the problem. We're allies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not allies. You are my subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:20.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I admit, you had the lot of us hoodwinked this entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:24.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You even gave our Generals a false motive\Nbehind your actions at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everything I said happened was the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:31.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I never harbored any ill will towards humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:37.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,From the day of your interview, it wasn't you\Nwho was being tested, but the Demon Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:44.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, do you have any regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:46.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't dodge the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:52.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was your one chance to die.\NYou may not get another for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:59.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you regret giving up potentially\Nyour only chance to be freed of your burdens?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:08.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-where did this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:16.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Back when we drank together.\NWhen I heard your story, I knew I wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:19.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wish to bring order to my world of chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To rid the land of conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:24.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want to make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:30.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want to help you find a way\Nfor humanity and demonkind to coexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:35.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here. I don't regret a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten that I am a villainous conqueror,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:43.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,one who invades other worlds\Nand wreaks havoc for her own gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:48.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you truly believe working beneath\Nsuch a villain would be virtuous?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:53.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,None of that's true. You're a kind queen\Nwho cares deeply for her people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:59.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That kindness drove you to invade\Nthe human world for the sake of your homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:03.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That kindness led you to empathize\Nwith the people you were conquering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's how I beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You love your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:10.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Conquest doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:14.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even now, you're asking me\Nthese things out of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:17.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You want me to know this\Nis my last chance to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that kindness of yours has saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:25.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let me help you, Echidna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:28.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll do everything in my power to ensure\Nyou never have to play the villain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:34.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To ensure you can be the kind queen\Nyou truly are, for all your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:39.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:46.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In three thousand years, I've never, ever made a girl cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:58.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I guess that's not true. But I'll uphold that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:09.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was going to give you one last chance,\Nbut it appears I've been misguided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hadn't expected you to repay me\Nwith such a purposeful new lease on life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I do like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:20.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you accept my answer, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:21.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:27.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to working with you, former hero Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:30.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It is an honor, Queen Echidna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:37.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was the story of how I came\Nto join the Demon Queen's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:41.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Father! Is General Edvard here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:46.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am so terribly sorry, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:50.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I deeply apologize for interrupting\Nyour romantic moment with Lord Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:54.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This was NOT a romantic moment, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Forget that! What did you come here for? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:03.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right! The wyverns are dissatisfied with\Ntheir treatment and have begun to riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:05.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right, you lot! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:11.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My deepest apologies, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We are awake, my Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:18.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Edvard, go deal with them before\Nthey cause any damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:19.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:22.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Scuse me, is General Lily here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:29.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Largo is complaining that the elixirs that\Nwere due yesterday haven't been delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,General Shutina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:37.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One of the tomes in the fourth library has run\Namok and is summoning a stream of chimeras!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:42.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That accursed tome again! I'm going to burn it\Nto a crisp, once and for all! Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernie, I was looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:47.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can't open the dining hall without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told you I was quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:51.25,Subtitle-4,,0,0,0,,I know, I know, but let's talk later! Come, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna, what should we\Ndo about the Great Spirit Portal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:58.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna, we've received a message\Nfrom the viceroy in the Demon World!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:06.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now, Leo, I believe you said you would\Ndo everything in your power to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:07.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As you can see, we have mountains of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:17.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Before we take on the large-scale issue\Nof uniting the human and demon realms,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:20.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,we'll need to tackle the problems we're currently facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I intend to make full use of your talents, so do be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't need to tell me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:30.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of it, so you sit back and have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:37.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was the story of how I came\Nto join the Demon Queen's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:43.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How the Hero Leo, a biological weapon\Ncreated three thousand years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:47.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,broke free of his ancient commands\Nto move forward on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:51.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How he made a great many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:55.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Friends he could trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:02.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How I finally, after all that time, was able to quit heroing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:10.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay. Where to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:28.25,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Bokura no kokoro wa itsudatte moroi\N{\rSong}Our hearts are always so frail and fragile{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:34.46,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Sore demo mae o muite nagai michi o susumu\N{\rSong}But we still face forward and continue down our long road{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:40.08,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Shiranakatta koto wa kore kara shireba ii\N{\rSong}If we don't know something now, we can go learn about it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:47.00,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Tsuzukeru koto no saki ni aru mono ima wa mada wakaranai kedo\N{\rSong}We might not know what's at the end of our long, continuing journey{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:53.17,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Hitori de kakaekomi suginaide tama ni wa senaka o azuketemiyou\N{\rSong}Don't try to do everything yourself, lean on us sometimes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:56.96,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Yowasa ni yorisoeru no mo tsuyosanara\N{\rSong}Sharing your weaknesses is strength in itself{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:23:01.38,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Madamada saki wa nagai kui no nai you ni\N{\rSong}There's still a long way to go,{\r}\N{\rSong}so make sure you won't regret anything{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:04.79,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Hashiridase riyuu wa tanjun\N{\rSong}Dash on! The reason's simple{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.79,0:23:08.25,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Tokihanate risou no yume o\N{\rSong}Let loose! Make your dreams reality{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:14.38,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Fumidashita saki no mirai wa jibun shidai de dou ni demo naru\N{\rSong}The future you're heading towards is one you shape yourself{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:20.17,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Kawaru koto ga kowakunattemo sukoshizutsu de iinda\N{\rSong}It's okay to be scared of change, you can go little by little{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.17,0:23:24.25,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Taisetsu na mono o mamoru tame ni\N{\rSong}I want to protect the things I cherish{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:26.83,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Megurimegutte tsunagatta\N{\rSong}(I'm so glad we found each other){\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.83,0:23:31.25,Song-2,,0,0,0,,Kimi ni arigatou todoiteimasu you ni\N{\rSong}So I hope you hear how thankful I am for you{\r}
